data.title: Chow mein is good
data.text: My husband liked the chow mein growing up so we came here for lunch Saturday. we ordered two combo plates. We loved the chow mein but were not fans of the orange chicken, beef n broccoli or the rice. It was hot inside so we werent able to eat comfortable. The worker was very nice and offered a to go bag. would return soley for chow mein..portions were very big..pricing was about 7 a combo.
